&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;This setting makes it possible to switch input method based on the context of cursor when entering insert mode.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>C-m, RET and Return Key in Emacs</title><link>https://fromkk.com/posts/c-m-ret-and-return-key-in-emacs/</link><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2020 21:23:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://fromkk.com/posts/c-m-ret-and-return-key-in-emacs/</guid><category domain="https://fromkk.com/categories/misc/">Misc</category><description>&lt;p&gt;I use Emacs to write blog. In the recent update, I found &lt;code&gt;M-RET&lt;/code&gt; no longer behave as leader key in org mode, but behave as &lt;code&gt;org-meta-return&lt;/code&gt;. And even more strange is that in other mode, it behave as leader key. And &lt;code&gt;M-RET&lt;/code&gt; also works in terminal in org mode. In GUI, pressing &lt;code&gt;C-M-m&lt;/code&gt; can trigger leader key.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SO I opened this &lt;a href="https://github.com/syl20bnr/spacemacs/issues/13374" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;issue&lt;/a&gt;, with the help of these friends, the issue has been fixed. Here is the cause of the bug.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Preview LaTeX in Org Mode with Emacs in MacOS</title><link>https://fromkk.com/posts/preview-latex-in-org-mode-with-emacs-in-macos/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2019 20:26:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://fromkk.com/posts/preview-latex-in-org-mode-with-emacs-in-macos/</guid><category domain="https://fromkk.com/categories/misc/">Misc</category><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="using-the-right-emacs-version"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Using the right Emacs Version&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a href="#using-the-right-emacs-version" class="heading-mark"&gt;
 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I failed to preview LaTeX with &lt;code&gt;emacs-plus&lt;/code&gt;. If you have installed &lt;code&gt;d12frosted/emacs-plus&lt;/code&gt;, uninstall it and use &lt;code&gt;emacs-mac&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>